article.headline: Chad Moodie leads Alabama A&M over NAIA member Oakwood 121-78 in season opener
article.description: — Chad Moodie had 13 points in Alabama A&M's 121-78 victory over NAIA member Oakwood on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Chad Moodie leads Alabama A&M over NAIA member Oakwood 121-78 in season opener
article.story: HUNTSVILLE, Ala. -- — Chad Moodie had 13 points in Alabama A&M's 121-78 victory over NAIA member Oakwood on Thursday night. Moodie added five rebounds for the Bulldogs. Dylan McLean shot 4 of 5 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line to add 12 points. EJay Greer had 11 points and shot 4 of 7 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line. Jordan Bell led the Ambassadors with 24 points, 10 rebounds, five assists and two steals. Nicholas Kennard added 15 points and Chase Jackson scored 11. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
